      "review_summary": "The branch changes memory sync resolution so unset watch is false for default gateway managers while preserving explicit, CLI, and status behavior, adds docs/tests, and also changes the OpenAI web-search Docker E2E lifecycle script.\n\nPR surface: Source +32, Tests +113, Docs +3. Total +148 across 11 files.\n\nReproducibility: yes. source-reproducible but not executed in this read-only review: current main resolves unset sync.watch to true, and the default builtin/QMD manager paths consume that setting for long-lived managers. The linked FD-pressure reports supply the production impact context.",
